nodes.text: Coris Mao was a male individual who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Sometime after 0 BBY, Coris Mao was stationed in Mos Entha. From here, Mao tasked a commando with the job killing many pirates and their boss in the Sand Pirate Base on Tatooine.
Coris Mao was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies.
